  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink230-kilavi">talaimakaṉ varaivu vēṇṭit tamarai viṭuttuḻi maṟuppar kollō veṉṟ accamuṟukiṉṟa talaivikkut tōḻi colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante said to the heroine, who was anxious that [her relatives] would refuse when the hero sent his relatives to ask for [her hand in] marriage. 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink230 ">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nammoṭu</l>
<l>ciṟutiṉaik kāvala ṉākip perituniṉ</l>
<l>meṉṟōṇ ñekiḻavun tirunutal pacappavum</l>
<l>poṉpōl viṟaṟkaviṉ ṟolaitta</l>
<l>kuṉṟa nāṭaṟ kayarvarnaṉ maṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Ah, friend,</l>
        <l>they will perform a good wedding [for you]</l>
        <l>to the man of the hills—</l>
        <l>[he who,]</l>
        <l>having become the guardian of small millet,</l> 
        <l>destroyed [your] gold-like, victorious beauty,</l>
        <l>for your tender shoulders to grow greatly emaciated</l>
        <l>and your lustrous forehead to become pale.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
